> root         0  0.0  0.0     0    0 ?        SW   Oct28   0:00 [bdflush]
> root         0  0.0  0.0     0    0 ?        SW   Oct28   0:01
> [kupdated]
>
> They seem to have PID 0, is this normal?
Yes. These are kernel threads.
